quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,6,"∆Åeen yeddu…ìe ngoon…óintaa foti a jeertinii …ìe wolla a jeertinaani, fof foti e mum en"
  2,7,"Alla muppi …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe, wirngallo woni noppi e gite ma…ì…ìe lette maw…óe na woodani …ìe"
  2,8,"Na woodi heen yim…ìe wi'oo…ìe min ngoon…óinii Alla e √±alaande wattan, tawa …ìe ngoon…óinaani"
  2,9,"E…ìe koda Alla e goon…óin…ìe …ìe, alaa mbo …ìe kodata sonaa ko'e ma…ì…ìe tawa …ìe nganndaa"
  2,10,Ko √±awo woni e …ìer…óe Alla …ìeydani …ìe √±awu maa lette muus…óe njan e mum en sabu ko …ìe pennannoo
  2,11,So …ìe mbi'aama taa bonnee e lesdi ndi …ìe mbi'a minen ko min mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe
  2,12,Ko kam…ìe tigi ngoni bonnoo…ìe kono …ìe tinataa …óum
  2,13,"So …ìe mbi'aama ngoon…óinee wano yim…ìe …ìee ngoon…óiri, …ìe mbi'a mbela minen ngoon…óina wano …óaay…ìe …ìee ngoon…óiniri, kono ko kam…ìe tigi ngoni …óaay…ìe kono …ìe nganndaa"
  2,14,"So tawii …ìe kawrii e goon…óin…ìe …ìe mbi'a: min ngoon…óinii, so …ìe njeewdii e sey…óanooji ma…ì…ìe …ói …ìe mbi'a: minen ko onon min ngonndi min njalkitat tan"
  2,15,Alla jalkita …ìe O …ìeydana …ìe bewre …ìe ngona e wemmbere
  2,16,"Ko …ìeen ngoni soodir…ìe peewal majjere njeeygu ma…ì…ìe alaa tono, te …ìe peewaano"
